linux-iprojection (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of iProjection (Unofficial) for Linux.
  * Native GTK4/Libadwaita user interface.
  * mDNS auto-discovery and PipeWire casting.
  * Direct ESC/VP advanced console and Wake-on-LAN support.

